<c74object name='sp.karplus~' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Extended Karplus-Strong resonant string model
</digest>
    <description>Extended Karplus-Strong resonant string model.
</description>
    <discussion><h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
The <o>sp.karplus~</o> object creates a flurry of triggers (or gates) after each input based on the current parameter settings. Can be used to trigger more processes down the line.
</discussion>

	<metadatalist>
		<metadata name='author'>Rodrigo Constanzo, Flucoma Project</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Machine Learning</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Audio Analysis</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Onset Detection</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Corpus Playback</metadata>
	</metadatalist>

